text: Miranda Kerr (born 20 April 1983) is an Australian writer and model. She became famous in 2007 as one of the Victoria's Secret angels. Kerr began modeling at age 13. She started several organic skincare products. Miranda Kerr was born in Sydney. ==References== Category:Australian models Category:Australian writers Category:1983 births Category:Living people Category:People from Sydney
